Request #4: Sex-based thresholds + correlated subquery (thrombosis_prediction)
Payload: {"question": "For all patients with normal uric acid (UA), what is the average UA index based on their latest laboratory examination result?", "db": "thrombosis_prediction"}
----------------------------------------
Response:
{"sql":"SELECT AVG(l.\"UA\") AS average_UA\nFROM \"Laboratory\" l\nINNER JOIN \"Patient\" p ON l.\"ID\" = p.\"ID\"\nWHERE l.\"UA\" BETWEEN 3.0 AND 7.0\n  AND l.\"Date\" = (\n    SELECT MAX(l2.\"Date\")\n    FROM \"Laboratory\" l2\n    WHERE l2.\"ID\" = l.\"ID\"\n  );","rows":[[4.593953488372093]],"iterations":1,"ok":true,"error":null,"history":[{"node":"generate_sql","sql":"SELECT AVG(l.\"UA\") AS average_UA\nFROM \"Laboratory\" l\nINNER JOIN \"Patient\" p ON l.\"ID\" = p.\"ID\"\nWHERE l.\"UA\" BETWEEN 3.0 AND 7.0\n  AND l.\"Date\" = (\n    SELECT MAX(l2.\"Date\")\n    FROM \"Laboratory\" l2\n    WHERE l2.\"ID\" = l.\"ID\"\n  );"}]}

